summary: Shane from Healthcare Solutions called Leanne Christman to review her Medicare benefits for 2025, focusing on potential $170 cash back and a flex card. He confirmed her Medicare parts A, B, and D, age (75), date of birth (11/19/1949), zip code (58504), and that she makes her own healthcare decisions. He then informed her that a licensed agent from her zip code would be brought on the call to discuss these benefits further, emphasizing no plan change, no extra cost, and that it would only take five minutes.
